</b></p>
<p><b>Persons with Disabilities and the Convention on the Elimination of All forms of 
</b></p>
<p><b>Discrimination against Women and consider ratifying other international 
</b></p>
<p><b>human rights conventions, particularly the International Covenant on 
</b></p>
<p><b>Economic, Social and Cultural Rights, the Convention on the Rights of the 
</b></p>
<p><b>Child and the International Convention on the Protection of the Rights of All 
</b></p>
<p><b>Migrant Workers and Members of their Families (Indonesia);  
</b></p>
