</b></p>
<p>176.67 <b>Ratify without delay the Rome Statute of the International Criminal 
</b></p>
<p><b>Court (Fiji); 
</b></p>
<p>176.68 <b>Take concrete steps towards ratifying the Rome Statute of the 
</b></p>
